OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Foil companies face grilling
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fby Congress                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Top oil executives have appeared before
OL,6, US lawmakers to face allegations they  
OL,7, misled the public about climate change.
OL,9,FMajor producers were quizzed about the 
OL,10,Fimpact of the fossil fuels they profit 
OL,11,Ffrom and their environmental toll.     
OL,13,FThe hearing on Thursday, which         
OL,14,FDemocrats hailed as historic, marked   
OL,15,Fthe first time oil bosses had answered 
OL,16,Fquestions publicly and under oath.     
OL,18,FThe six-hour session saw some heated   
OL,19,Fexchanges, with firms such as BP and   
OL,20,FShell facing tough questions.          
